  # Discord Bot Demo

## Features
- /profile — Save a nickname
- /show — Show your nickname
- Simple landing page describing the bot

## Setup
1. Install Node.js (v18+)
2. Clone the repo
3. Run `npm install`
4. Add your bot token in Replit Secrets or `.env` as `BOT_TOKEN`
5. Run `node bot.js` to start
6. Invite the bot to your server with OAuth2 URL

## Hosting
- Free: Replit (bot), GitHub Pages / Netlify (landing page)
- Paid: VPS or cloud hosting for 24/7 uptime
